      "content": "Yeah, you'll definitely lose a lot of that nuance. But honestly, the enterprise clients are mostly just looking for quick, standard responses these days, so the energy savings are the priority for the company right now. It's just the way the budget and the green initiatives are moving. It's all part of the scheduled decommissioning process.",
